metadata.cwe: CWE-330: Use of Insufficiently Random Values
metadata.description: The App uses an insecure Random Number Generator.

metadata.cwe: CWE-312: Cleartext Storage of Sensitive Information
metadata.description: Files may contain hardcoded sensitive information like usernames, passwords, keys etc.

metadata.cwe: CWE-532: Insertion of Sensitive Information into Log File
metadata.description: The App logs information. Sensitive information should never be logged.
This App uses SSL certificate pinning to detect or  prevent MITM attacks in secure communication channel.

metadata.cwe: CWE-89: Improper Neutralization of Special Elements used in an SQL Command ('SQL Injection')
metadata.description: App uses SQLite Database and execute raw SQL query. Untrusted user input in raw SQL queries can cause SQL Injection. Also sensitive information should be encrypted and written to the database.

metadata.cwe: CWE-749: Exposed Dangerous Method or Function
metadata.description: Insecure WebView Implementation. Execution of user controlled code in WebView is a critical Security Hole.
Ensure that user controlled URLs never reaches the Webview. Enabling file access from URLs in WebView can leak sensitive information from the file system.
This App may have root detection capabilities.
App can write to App Directory. Sensitive Information should be encrypted.
App can read/write to External Storage. Any App can read data written to External Storage.

metadata.cwe: CWE-327: Use of a Broken or Risky Cryptographic Algorithm
metadata.description: SHA-1 is a weak hash known to have hash collisions.

metadata.cwe: CWE-649: Reliance on Obfuscation or Encryption of Security-Relevant Inputs without Integrity Checking
metadata.description: The App uses the encryption mode CBC with PKCS5/PKCS7 padding. This configuration is vulnerable to padding oracle attacks.

playstore_details.title: Life Time Digital
playstore_details.description:
UNLIMITED ACCESS TO FITNESS, HEALTH & WELLNESS — ANYTIME, ANYWHERE — NO CLUB MEMBERSHIP REQUIRED
Download the Life Time Digital app and unlock the ultimate destination for your healthiest, happiest life. At home, at the gym, or on the go, enjoy world-class fitness classes, expert nutrition plans, guided meditations, podcasts, and lifestyle programs — all in one seamless experience.

L•AI•C – THE FUTURE OF HEALTHY LIVING
Meet L•AI•C (“lay-see”), your personal wellness companion — powered by AI, backed by Life Time expertise, and designed to help you live smarter and healthier. More than an assistant, L•AI•C is your coach, guide, concierge, and motivator — tailored to you.
•  Personalized Plans, Real Results. Dynamic workouts built for your goals, schedule, and lifestyle. Whether training for a race, building strength, or improving sleep, she keeps you moving forward.
•  Expert Answers, Instantly. Tap into Life Time’s expertise. Ask anything — “How do I recover faster?” “What’s a high-protein breakfast?” — and get actionable advice in seconds.
• A Concierge That Gets You. Find classes, reserve courts, schedule appointments, and discover experiences — personalized to your habits, schedule, and club events.

FOR EVERYONE
PREMIUM FITNESS & WELLNESS, ANYWHERE
• Stream unlimited on-demand and live fitness classes led by top instructors — including strength, cardio, yoga, barre, HIIT, cycling, and more.
• Explore workout programs tailored to goals like weight loss, strength training, active aging, and healthy habit formation.
• Enjoy workouts and fitness plans that adapt to your level and schedule.

PERSONALIZED NUTRITION & HEALTH COACHING
• Follow nutrition plans and healthy meal guides crafted by certified experts.
• Get hyper-personalized workouts curated by L•AI•C—Life Time’s intelligent wellness companion—based on your goals, preferences, and lifestyle.
• Build sustainable routines that support your body, mind, and lifestyle.

 MIND & BODY WELLNESS TOOLS
• Access guided meditations, breathwork, recovery sessions, and sleep support.
• Listen to full episodes of the Life Time Talks podcast for inspiration on health, wellness, mindset, and motivation.
• Read exclusive articles from Experience Life Magazine on longevity, stress, mental health, and holistic living.

ATHLETIC EVENTS & RACE TOOLS
• Find and Register for Events – Discover Life Time’s premier athletic events nationwide—marathons, cycling races, triathlons, and more—all in one place.
• Race Training & Recovery Plans – Get expert-designed training programs to boost endurance, improve performance, and speed up recovery for your next race.
• Digital Race Pass & Easy Check-In – Skip the lines with your digital race pass and check in seamlessly at Life Time events.
• Track & Share Race Results – Instantly find, claim, and share your official race results directly in the app.

LIFESHOP – WELLNESS & FITNESS ESSENTIALS
• Trusted Supplements – Fuel your goals with premium formulas like D.Tox, magnesium, electrolytes, protein, greens, and more.
• Activewear & Recovery Gear – Find top-rated apparel and gear for training, performance, and recovery.
• Earn Rewards – Get 5% back on every in-app purchase as a Life Time app user.

FOR CLUB MEMBERS
ENHANCED FEATURES FOR OUR CLUB MEMBERS
• Check in to the club and sign up for events.
•  Reserve classes, camps, and more.
•  Order from the café, bistro, or book LifeSpa services.
